# Description
#
# Uses the ls command with arguments:
# ls - list
#
# p - Stream output format accross page, comma delimited 
#
# t - sort by time modified
#
# m - Write slash after filename if file is directory
#
# Usage: bash path/to/midLS 
#
#########################################
ls -trhpm
